<li>Honorary doctorate, <a href="/wiki/University_of_Maryland,_College_Park" title="University of Maryland, College Park">University of Maryland, College Park</a>, 2004</li>
<li>Honorary doctorate, <a href="/wiki/University_of_Toronto" title="University of Toronto">University of Toronto</a>, 2004</li>
